			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Declaration note from Giraldo Nobre Ferreira, a student, to  a non identified addressee.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The authors declares that he will serve the devil.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">Giraldo Nobre Ferreira was a Theology student in Braga, the son of a trader. He was arrested in 1720 because he had written a note where he invoked the devil. He explained that he was desperate to gain the affection of a woman and wrote the note in order to conquer her. He was sentenced to exile in the extreme South of Portugal, in Castro Marim, Algarve.</p>
				<p sameAs="text"></p></change>
		</revisionDesc>
